ğŸš€ How to Run Locally
Download or clone the project
Open terminal and install backend dependencies:
cd backend
npm install
Set up your MongoDB Atlas URI in .env file:
MONGODB_URI=your_mongo_uri Run backend server:

node server.js Open index.html from the frontend folder in a browser.
